      "content": "i get that it's not ideal but i'm not even drunk, just like a tiny bit of wine. i've heard from some people that a little bit of booze actually helps the meds work better since they both work on the same part of the brain. is there really a big risk if it's just one glass? it feels like overkill to avoid it entirely when i'm this exhausted",
